    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u> </u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/06822e734edf226b2f9a0e0c94867591.avif?t=1732791590\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As players unravel the mysteries, they collect individual words—one for each level. Once all 12 words are revealed, they form the Recovery Phrase - password.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the biggest puzzle contest for players! Whoever solves the puzzles first and deciphers the entire Recovery Phrase, wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/571aa34167da177e66362d662f8bc1bd.avif?t=1732791590\" width=616 height=157 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Camera Mode.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take photos with an in-game camera and store them alongside your notes.<br>Capture and keep track of important details from puzzle levels, making it easier to stay on course and solve challenges efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/b08ae983fbbf81dd3e34f4e67e7743fd.poster.avif?t=1732791590\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/b08ae983fbbf81dd3e34f4e67e7743fd.webm?t=1732791590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/b08ae983fbbf81dd3e34f4e67e7743fd.mp4?t=1732791590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Write your notes.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To remember what you've found and piece together the mysteries more effectively. Whether it’s a clever insight or a crucial detail, your notes will be your best companion on the path to victory.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/be28496c79cba39e56941fbce86b9efb.poster.avif?t=1732791590\" width=609 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/be28496c79cba39e56941fbce86b9efb.webm?t=1732791590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Players aren’t limited to pen and paper. They can leverage modern tools.    </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Using AI</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wikipedia</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Analyzing satellite data</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every resource is fair game!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/18de31b29806b6c203940beec7866d3b.poster.avif?t=1732791590\" width=609 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/18de31b29806b6c203940beec7866d3b.webm?t=1732791590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Think outside the box!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This feature encourages creativity and pushes you to think beyond the game screen and find unique solutions. Sometimes, the solution isn’t spelled out in the game. It resides within your mind, waiting to be pieced together. Trust your instincts; they might lead you to victory.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/160a004d99a6b54e771acf88d0fc1b83.poster.avif?t=1732791590\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/160a004d99a6b54e771acf88d0fc1b83.webm?t=1732791590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181630/extras/160a004d99a6b54e771acf88d0fc1b83.mp4?t=1732791590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Whether you're a young beginner or an experienced veteran, our game is designed to be a challenge for all players.</p>",
